            {
                "comment": "Professor Munchmeyer is very nice and knows the topics he teaches very well. He keeps lectures light with jokes occasionally but does not overdo it. His lectures are based off of his lecture slides he posts, which are very detailed and the best slides I have seen from a professor. He makes very few errors and is sure to correct them if he does.",
